      }
    },
    "You can set it up by going to Settings → Apps → Side Search and turning on \"Press Side Button for Side Search\"." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "設定 → アプリ → Side Searchで「サイドボタンを押してSide Searchを使用」をオンにすることで設定できます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You can use the app's URL scheme for the Search URL. If you set the assistant to Open in Default App, you can also use Universal Links." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
